# This git repo is located at the home directory.
# Ignore everything by default, then allow only Cardano_Staking data artifacts.
*

# Keep git control files
!.gitignore

# Keep Cardano-Staking project folder visible
!Cardano-Staking/

# Track only the Cardano staking analysis subtree
!Cardano-Staking/Data_Analysis/
!Cardano-Staking/Data_Analysis/**

# Tokenomics must live in a separate repository
Cardano-Staking/Tokenomic-CIP50/
